      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand. my doctor is actually super busy and i probably won't be able to get a hold of them until next week. if i just take a smaller dose of the simvastatin while i'm on the clarithromycin, like half a pill instead of my usual one, would that be a safe way to bridge the gap without stopping it completely?",
